name: amazon-star-widget
description: <!-- https://leetcode.com/discuss/interview-question/546992/amazon-phone-front-end-engineer-ii --> Basic takeaway is that, in spite of what the recruiter says, FEE interviews are different material than SDE interviews. This caught me off guard as I had studied algos, data structures, etc. Recruiter said "all engineers at Amazon are interviewed on the same material". Not really the case in my experience.... Hope this helps others.
author: abhinav
